of the Spankers.
[Audience laughing]

56:03.694 --> 56:05.930
Damn, sir, if you don't appear
to be related

56:05.963 --> 56:08.933
To every family
in Great Britain.
[Foot stomping]

56:08.966 --> 56:13.471
[Muffled laughter,
door creaking]

56:13.504 --> 56:16.974
Oh! Mr. Woodward.
Good evening.

56:17.675 --> 56:19.877
We were expecting you
this morning.

56:19.910 --> 56:22.079
Mrs. Davenport,
we've been on foot

56:22.112 --> 56:23.914
