Adira's been ill.

56:23.948 --> 56:27.017
Aw, I'm so sorry.
Please,

56:27.051 --> 56:29.454
Come and make yourself
as comfortable as possible.
[Adira coughing]

56:29.487 --> 56:31.088
And Rose...

56:31.121 --> 56:33.791
- You need some rest.
- No, Rose, sustenance.

56:33.824 --> 56:36.727
Please, sit down.
Sit, sit.
[Distant chatter]

56:39.229 --> 56:41.098
We didn't hear from Garrett
and we're worried.

56:41.866 --> 56:43.067
(Samuel)
We got away on a train.

56:44.535 --> 56:45.870
Is someone following you?

56:45.903 --> 56:48.873
Yes sir... ma'am,
by the name of Plimpton.

56:49.474 --> 56:51.976
Plimpton?
He's back?

56:52.743 --> 56:54.011
Oh, fiddlesticks!

56:55.546 --> 56:56.781
Oh, don't mind me, dears.
[Fabric rustling]

56:57.247 --> 56:59.650
Uh, my husband,
Mr. Barney Fagan.

56:59.684 --> 57:01.018
Esquire.

57:01.051 --> 57:03.988
It's plan B now, darling.
Think graveyard scenario.

57:04.021 --> 57:05.723
Oh, yes, that's always
a crowd pleaser.

57:05.756 --> 57:07.558
You'll have to bunk down
with us here tonight.

57:07.592 --> 57:09.727
Yes, there are men
watching the hall

57:09.760 --> 57:11.529
And we can't be too careful.

57:11.562 --> 57:15.966
Barney, as you can see, thinks
that men are spying on us.

57:16.000 --> 57:18.569
