I saw them in the alleyway.
[Fanny chuckling]

57:18.603 --> 57:20.971
But he's always been
a paranoid performer.

57:22.707 --> 57:24.809
My dear, we are slaves
to the critics.

57:25.275 --> 57:27.778
[Adira laughing in delight]

57:29.514 --> 57:31.716
Oh...
[Barney laughing]

57:33.283 --> 57:36.020
[Slow footsteps]

57:36.887 --> 57:38.689
I promise you

57:38.723 --> 57:40.858
We will get you across the line
before tomorrow night

57:41.158 --> 57:42.793
Saturday at the latest.

57:43.994 --> 57:46.263
And tomorrow

57:46.296 --> 57:48.699
Creeping its petty pace
from day to day

57:48.733 --> 57:51.268
To the last syllable
of recorded time.

57:51.301 --> 57:54.505
And all our yesterdays
have lighted fools

57:54.539 --> 57:56.807
The way to dusty death.

57:57.174 --> 58:00.945
[Audience applauding]

58:00.978 --> 58:02.613
(Fanny)
We'll do the best we can.

58:02.647 --> 58:05.850
Yes, and we have a cast
of supernumeraries

58:05.883 --> 58:06.984
Just for the occasion.

58:07.017 --> 58:13.658
[Audience applauding excitedly]

58:16.894 --> 58:21.832
[Audience whistling]
[And cheering]

58:26.637 --> 58:28.939
(Barney)
And then I said,
ask the Bengal tiger!

58:28.973 --> 58:30.541
He's the one that ate him!

58:30.575 --> 58:33.744
[Laughter]

58:33.778 --> 58:36.280
