01:04:39.643 --> 01:04:41.178
Here are your instructions.

01:04:41.645 --> 01:04:43.981
Thank you, Mrs. Davenport.

01:04:44.014 --> 01:04:47.351
Here, Vanessa.
I wore it as Portia.

01:04:48.185 --> 01:04:50.220
- It's yours.
- Keep it hidden, my dear.

01:04:51.521 --> 01:04:54.524
Now, you'd better hurry.
There's quite a tempest brewing
[Thunder rumbling]

01:04:54.558 --> 01:04:56.593
And we have to bury our dead.

01:04:56.626 --> 01:04:57.928
Thank you, sir.

01:04:57.962 --> 01:04:59.529
Reverend Douglass
will see you through.

01:05:00.330 --> 01:05:01.966
Get up! Go on.

01:05:03.267 --> 01:05:05.335
(Barney)
Bye. Travel safely.

